        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2784474743" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16531935538465913705">Another very interesting tale about the culture of Florence. When a young woman is kidnapped, her friend is released. The problem is why? Marshal Guarnaccia takes on the case, which proves to be much more complex than it appeared at first. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


